(5) each
date on which the principal of the Debt Securities will be
payable;

(6) the
interest rate that the Debt Securities will bear and the interest
payment dates for the Debt Securities;

(7) each
place where payments on the Debt Securities will be
payable;

(8) any
terms upon which the Debt Securities may be redeemed, in whole or
in part, at our option;

(9) any
